    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've seen enough doctors. they just give me more pills that don't work and tell me to \"manage\" it. there is no managing this. it's just a cycle of waking up in pain and waiting to go back to sleep just so i don't have to feel my own body for a few hours. it feels like there's no point to any of it anymore.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
