      "content": "support groups don't fix the nerves. they just talk about how bad it is. i don't want to \"manage\" this feeling for the next thirty years. i just want it to be over. sometimes i think the only real kindness left is just... lettting go. like, wouldn't it be more merciful to just not exist than to live like this?",
